title: Operation Petticoat
description: A veteran naval commander is given command of a submarine full of misfits, miscreants and with a group of nurses as passengers.

title: Yeoman Hunkle, Yeoman Hunkle Part 1
description: The old submarine,Sea Tiger is finally sent on a real mission after several errand jobs. Their task is to attack an abandoned Japanese ammo dump to take explosives that the US desperately needs.
